        y - the row
        n - the number of the escape sector

      • refreshPosition

        public void refreshPosition()
        Method to set the new current position of the player, which we indicated with a red glow over the sector. Ask what is the current position of the player and if it's different from the one the panel was saving before than we delete the red glow of the old position and put it over the new sector.
